# Performance Analysis and Bottlenecks

**Identifying system limitations and constraints**

| Component | Current Performance | Target Performance | Bottleneck Level |
|-----------|-------------------|-------------------|------------------|
| **API Response Time** | 350ms average | <{{performance_target}} | High |
| **Database Queries** | 2.5s complex queries | <500ms | Critical |
| **Transaction Processing** | 25K TPS peak | {{transaction_volume}} | High |
| **Memory Utilization** | 85% average | <70% | Medium |
| **CPU Usage** | 78% peak | <60% | Medium |
| **Storage I/O** | 950 IOPS | 2000+ IOPS | Critical |

**Overall Performance Rating: 4.2/10 - Significant improvement required**

@notes:
- Performance metrics show specific problem areas
- Database and storage I/O most critical bottlenecks
- API response time affects user experience
- Target metrics provide clear improvement goals

